items.name: Total Drama Wiki
items.title: Total Drama Wiki
items.headline: Live the action on the Total Drama Wiki
items.desc: Founded on July 6, 2008, the Total Drama Wiki is a collaborative wiki focusing on Total Drama, a franchise that lampoon the conventions commonly found in reality shows. It premiered on the Canadian television channel Teletoon, on July 8, 2007 and the American television channel Cartoon Network, on June 5, 2008. Make sure to check our wiki for all the details on Total Drama.

items.name: Total Drama Island Fanfiction wikia
items.title: Total Drama Island Fanfiction wikia
items.headline: The Total Drama Fanfiction Wiki
items.desc: The Total Drama Fanfiction Wiki is a website dedicated to creating fanfictions centered around Total Drama, which is a Canadian animated "show within a show" television series that parodies reality television. This wiki is a collaborative community of users, allowing any user to add and edit stories and other content in accordance with our guidelines.

items.headline: Come visit the Total Drama Camps Wiki!
items.desc: Here, at the Total Drama Camps Wiki, users may roleplay camps, mainly based on Total Drama, Survivor, Big Brother, and other formats, meet new users and friends, chat, and have fun! Our wiki was born in 2009, and it continues to be successful to this very day. Come join the wiki, and we'll accept you with open arms! Make camps, compete, vote, win.

items.headline: Total Drama Smackdown!
items.desc: Total Drama Smackdown is where 13 contestants spend 12 weeks at an abandonned shopping mall. Last player standing wins $1,000,000. The first season airs on Friday Septemeber 7th. If you wish to enter a character for Season 2, entries close September 30. You can enter as many characters as you want on this show!
